WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.580
Environmental pollution has far reaching consequences

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:05.780
for community health.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:09.540
While industrial emissions and waste disposal

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:12.140
contribute to air and water pollution,

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:16.040
the adverse health effects on residents include

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:19.140
respiratory diseases and other chronic illnesses.

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:23.100
Implementing stricter environmental regulations

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:26.291
is essential to safeguard public health.
